{
  "description": "A breathtaking view of a vast, green meadow framed by towering, rocky cliffs and dense coniferous forests under a bright blue sky with scattered white clouds. The cliffs rise dramatically, revealing layers of grey stone and patches of green vegetation clinging to their faces. The meadow is lush and covered in vibrant green grass, punctuated by scattered trees. The trees appear to be predominantly pine and fir, creating a dense, dark green canopy. In the distant background, a snow-capped mountain peak is partially obscured by clouds, adding to the scene's majestic scale. The overall impression is one of pristine natural beauty and immense geological power.",
